-- A Light MVC framework to PHP --

// Folder description
/apis    mapping route rule present layer code base
/app     system main entrance and related config 
/core    system lib and func place
/stores  business logic, Controller and Model 
/vendor  composer manage thrid-party application
/web.static   (option) static file place, such as images, js, css or upload file   
/web.view     (option) server-side rander place